  "text": "All patients were in complete clinical remission at the time of study enrollment. Although not the study end point, time to treatment failure was defined based on data from Rustin et al. [CITATION_1] . Treatment failure was characterized by (a ) physical examination evidence of disease recurrence or (b) radiographic evidence of disease recurrence (biopsy will be done at the discretion of the principal investigator but is not required).",
